# Simple Job Application API

This is an API for simple job application system. It is built using the [Express](https://expressjs.com/) framework, [PostgreSQL](https://www.postgresql.org/) database using [Prisma](https://www.prisma.io/) ORM and [TypeScript](https://www.typescriptlang.org/).

### Clone repo

### Apply migrations

```sh
prisma migrate deploy
```

### Configure environment variables

- rename .env.example to .env
- add database url
- add secret key
- add port

### Run development server

```sh
yarn dev
```

### Run production server

```sh
yarn build
yarn start
```
